{"tid":1169482,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"少年下體拔不出！動用電鋸切鐵管火花四濺","createTime":"2019-05-24T12:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T04:21:04.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e5ec270b8d225d40872a45c2f91faa0e846ccf","tid":1169482,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞柔北東甲區的1名少年，昨晚將自己的下體放入1截鐵管內，結果無法拿出，最後勞動消拯隊來幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《詩華日報》報導，事件發生於約在昨晚10點，這名16歲的少年，昨天晚上在家中一時興起，將自己的下體，放入1根約15公分長的鐵管之中，但後來去無法取出，家人發現後，連忙打電話請消拯隊來救援。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，消拯隊到場後，嘗試各種方法，都無法幫助少年脫困，於是只好動用電鋸將鐵管切斷，現場火花四濺，但少年的下體，卻仍然卡在鐵管內，只好將他送醫。<br />\n<br />\n消息中說，後來在醫院內，醫護人員花了約1個小時，才讓少年與鐵管分開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190523/640_a69a34f8d5d11bd51dbe5da33354da92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190523%2F640_a69a34f8d5d11bd51dbe5da33354da92.jpg&h=7de17b98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faa5b79eab0eb24de6459fb3116cb771766b1442","tid":1169482,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"廢 !  兒登仔扯到恆 谷爆條管啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f75f971030b9b0fa6d0b6e2cf2ee9b8f8bf17ce","tid":1169482,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:55:16.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"f028b79bf206bf3805b367b1efd796b804f94b99","tid":1169482,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />活塞男"},{"pid":"1713880adb930ebfdfcdc73a2a4d971b99913357","tid":1169482,"uid":69568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"又要玩活塞男D花名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src